    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鬼眼》（<strong>The Haunting Eyes</strong>）是一款将你带到一座豪宅的游戏，20 年前，这里发生了一件只有你知道的悲惨事件。你，丹尼尔，是一个死于丈夫之手的女孩最好的朋友。丹尼尔答应了最后一个案子，并来到了那里，但谁又知道这座豪宅隐藏着什么秘密呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索这座宅邸。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075250/extras/9226febfd3e260bdcdf184a1e8647dad.avif?t=1741208873\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>当心！这个古老而被人遗忘的地方已成为每一个来到这里的人的噩梦。古老的走廊、呼啸的风声、吱呀作响的门和远处传来的尖叫声。漫步这座宅邸，了解它的历史。这里究竟隐藏着什么？</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >尝试在鬼魂中生存。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075250/extras/51dc360b9a993596076eb1ee19c345c2.avif?t=1741208873\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>安静 我想... 它已经来了！它是来找你报仇的......”</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >让自己沉浸在带有精美场景的完整故事中。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075250/extras/fb0e8f52d3611ad8767fe7350e631fde.avif?t=1741208873\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>了解丹尼尔的遭遇 这个被遗忘的可怕宅邸里到底潜藏着什么？是什么让大家无法平静地生活？</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075250/extras/9bd6f47e2871d7658b5205482393bc70.avif?t=1741208873\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075250/extras_big/9bd6f47e2871d7658b5205482393bc70.avif?t=1741208873 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
